        {"title": "实现密码强度检查器", "description": "编写函数check_password_strength(password)，检查密码强度。\n\n弱: <8字符\n中: 8-11字符，包含字母和数字\n强: >=12字符，包含字母数字特殊字符", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def check_password_strength(password):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"abc123!@#xyz\", \"expected\": \"strong\"}]", "solution": "def check_password_strength(password):\n    length = len(password)\n    has_letter = any(c.isalpha() for c in password)\n    has_digit = any(c.isdigit() for c in password)\n    has_special = any(not c.isalnum() for c in password)\n    if length < 8: return weak\n    if length >= 12 and has_letter and has_digit and has_special: return strong\n    if has_letter and has_digit: return medium\n    return weak", "hint": "检查长度和字符类型"},
        {"title": "实现CSRF Token生成器", "description": "编写函数generate_csrf_token(session_id)，生成CSRF Token。\n\n使用session_id和随机数生成token", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "CSRF", "code_template": "def generate_csrf_token(session_id):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"abc123\", \"expected\": \"token string\"}]", "solution": "def generate_csrf_token(session_id):\n    import hashlib\n    import time\n    data = f\"{session_id}{time.time()}\"\n    return hashlib.sha256(data.encode()).hexdigest()", "hint": "使用哈希函数生成唯一token"},
