        {"title": "实现文件类型验证器", "description": "编写函数validate_file_type(filename, allowed_extensions)，验证文件类型。\n\n返回valid或invalid", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def validate_file_type(filename, allowed_extensions):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"test.jpg, [jpg,png,gif]\", \"expected\": \"valid\"}]", "solution": "def validate_file_type(filename, allowed_extensions):\n    ext = filename.rsplit('.', 1)[-1].lower() if '.' in filename else ''\n    if ext in allowed_extensions: return valid\n    return invalid", "hint": "提取扩展名后检查"},
        {"title": "实现敏感信息脱敏器", "description": "编写函数mask_sensitive(data, type)，对敏感信息脱敏。\n\nphone: 保留前3后4\nemail: 保留首字母和域名\nid_card: 保留前4后4", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "敏感信息泄露", "code_template": "def mask_sensitive(data, type):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"13812345678, phone\", \"expected\": \"138****5678\"}]", "solution": "def mask_sensitive(data, type):\n    if type == phone: return data[:3] + '****' + data[-4:]\n    if type == email:\n        name, domain = data.split('@')\n        return name[0] + '***@' + domain\n    if type == id_card: return data[:4] + '****' + data[-4:]\n    return data", "hint": "根据类型选择脱敏规则"},
        {"title": "实现暴力破解检测器", "description": "编写函数detect_brute_force(login_attempts, threshold, window_seconds)，检测暴力破解。\n\nlogin_attempts: list of {timestamp, success}\n返回是否触发暴力破解警报", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "认证漏洞", "code_template": "def detect_brute_force(login_attempts, threshold, window_seconds):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"attempts, 5, 300\", \"expected\": \"detected or normal\"}]", "solution": "def detect_brute_force(login_attempts, threshold, window_seconds):\n    import time\n    now = time.time()\n    recent_fails = [a for a in login_attempts if now - a[timestamp] < window_seconds and not a[success]]\n    if len(recent_fails) >= threshold: return detected\n    return normal", "hint": "统计时间窗口内失败次数"},
        {"title": "实现安全头检查器", "description": "编写函数check_security_headers(headers)，检查响应安全头。\n\n检查: X-Frame-Options, CSP, HSTS, X-Content-Type-Options\n返回缺失的安全头列表", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def check_security_headers(headers):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"{X-Frame-Options:DENY}\", \"expected\": \"[CSP,HSTS,X-Content-Type-Options]\"}]", "solution": "def check_security_headers(headers):\n    required = ['X-Frame-Options', 'Content-Security-Policy', 'Strict-Transport-Security', 'X-Content-Type-Options']\n    return [h for h in required if h not in headers]", "hint": "检查必需的安全头是否存在"},
        {"title": "实现JWT Token验证器", "description": "编写函数validate_jwt_format(token)，验证JWT格式。\n\nJWT格式: header.payload.signature\n返回valid或invalid_format", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "认证漏洞", "code_template": "def validate_jwt_format(token):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"eyJhb.eyJzd.abc\", \"expected\": \"valid\"}]", "solution": "def validate_jwt_format(token):\n    parts = token.split('.')\n    if len(parts) != 3: return invalid_format\n    if not all(parts): return invalid_format\n    return valid", "hint": "JWT由3个.分隔的base64部分组成"},
        {"title": "实现IP白名单检查", "description": "编写函数check_ip_whitelist(client_ip, whitelist)，检查IP是否在白名单中。\n\n返回allowed或denied", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def check_ip_whitelist(client_ip, whitelist):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"192.168.1.1, [192.168.1.1,10.0.0.1]\", \"expected\": \"allowed\"}]", "solution": "def check_ip_whitelist(client_ip, whitelist):\n    if client_ip in whitelist: return allowed\n    return denied", "hint": "直接检查IP是否在列表中"},
        {"title": "实现URL安全检查", "description": "编写函数check_url_safety(url)，检查URL是否安全。\n\n不安全: 包含javascript:, data:, 或重定向到外部域名\n返回safe或unsafe", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def check_url_safety(url):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"javascript:alert(1)\", \"expected\": \"unsafe\"}]", "solution": "def check_url_safety(url):\n    lower = url.lower()\n    if lower.startswith('javascript:') or lower.startswith('data:'): return unsafe\n    if '//' in lower and not lower.startswith('http://') and not lower.startswith('https://'): return unsafe\n    return safe", "hint": "检查危险的URL协议"},
        {"title": "实现命令注入检测器", "description": "编写函数detect_command_injection(input_str)，检测命令注入。\n\n检测: ;, |, &, $, `等命令分隔符\ndangerous或safe", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def detect_command_injection(input_str):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"test; rm -rf /\", \"expected\": \"dangerous\"}]", "solution": "def detect_command_injection(input_str):\n    dangerous_chars = [';', '|', '&', '$', '`', '\\n']\n    for c in dangerous_chars:\n        if c in input_str: return dangerous\n    return safe", "hint": "检查命令分隔符"},
        {"title": "实现密码哈希函数", "description": "编写函数hash_password(password, salt)，使用SHA256加盐哈希密码。\n\n返回哈希值的十六进制字符串", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def hash_password(password, salt):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"mypassword, randomsalt\", \"expected\": \"hash string\"}]", "solution": "def hash_password(password, salt):\n    import hashlib\n    data = f\"{salt}{password}\"\n    return hashlib.sha256(data.encode()).hexdigest()", "hint": "盐值拼接密码后哈希"},
        {"title": "实现CORS配置检查器", "description": "编写函数check_cors_config(origin, allowed_origins)，检查CORS配置。\n\n返回allowed或blocked", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def check_cors_config(origin, allowed_origins):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"https://example.com, [https://example.com]\", \"expected\": \"allowed\"}]", "solution": "def check_cors_config(origin, allowed_origins):\n    if '*' in allowed_origins: return allowed\n    if origin in allowed_origins: return allowed\n    return blocked", "hint": "检查来源是否在允许列表中"},
        {"title": "实现请求频率限制器", "description": "编写函数rate_limit_check(client_id, requests, max_per_minute)，检查请求频率。\n\n返回allowed或rate_limited", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def rate_limit_check(client_id, requests, max_per_minute):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"client1, [t1,t2,t3], 10\", \"expected\": \"allowed\"}]", "solution": "def rate_limit_check(client_id, requests, max_per_minute):\n    import time\n    now = time.time()\n    recent = [r for r in requests if now - r < 60]\n    if len(recent) >= max_per_minute: return rate_limited\n    return allowed", "hint": "统计最近一分钟的请求数"},
        {"title": "实现路径遍历检测", "description": "编写函数detect_path_traversal(path)，检测路径遍历攻击。\n\n检测: ../, ..\\, %2e%2e\n返回dangerous或safe", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "OWASP Top 10", "code_template": "def detect_path_traversal(path):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"../../../etc/passwd\", \"expected\": \"dangerous\"}]", "solution": "def detect_path_traversal(path):\n    patterns = ['../', '..\\\\', '%2e%2e', '..%2f']\n    lower = path.lower()\n    for p in patterns:\n        if p in lower: return dangerous\n    return safe", "hint": "检查路径遍历常见模式"},
        {"title": "实现Cookie安全检查", "description": "编写函数check_cookie_security(cookie)，检查Cookie安全属性。\n\n检查: Secure, HttpOnly, SameSite\n返回缺失的属性列表", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def check_cookie_security(cookie):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"session=abc; Secure\", \"expected\": \"[HttpOnly, SameSite]\"}]", "solution": "def check_cookie_security(cookie):\n    required = ['Secure', 'HttpOnly', 'SameSite']\n    return [attr for attr in required if attr.lower() not in cookie.lower()]", "hint": "检查安全属性是否存在"},
        {"title": "实现日志安全审计", "description": "编写函数audit_log(log_entries)，审计安全日志。\n\n检测可疑行为: 多次登录失败、异常时间访问\n返回可疑事件列表", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "渗透测试方法论", "code_template": "def audit_log(log_entries):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"[{event:login_fail},{event:login_fail},{event:login_fail}]\", \"expected\": \"[brute_force_suspected]\"}]", "solution": "def audit_log(log_entries):\n    suspicious = []\n    fail_count = sum(1 for e in log_entries if e.get('event') == 'login_fail')\n    if fail_count >= 3: suspicious.append('brute_force_suspected')\n    night_access = [e for e in log_entries if e.get('hour', 12) < 6]\n    if night_access: suspicious.append('unusual_time_access')\n    return suspicious", "hint": "统计失败次数和异常时间"},
        {"title": "实现加密解密工具", "description": "编写函数simple_encrypt(text, key)和simple_decrypt(cipher, key)，实现简单加密。\n\n使用异或加密", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def simple_encrypt(text, key):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"hello, 3\", \"expected\": \"encrypted string\"}]", "solution": "def simple_encrypt(text, key):\n    return ''.join(chr(ord(c) ^ key) for c in text)\ndef simple_decrypt(cipher, key):\n    return ''.join(chr(ord(c) ^ key) for c in cipher)", "hint": "异或加密可逆"},
        {"title": "实现漏洞评分计算器", "description": "编写函数calculate_cvss(base_score, temporal_factor, environmental_factor)，计算CVSS评分。\n\n最终分 = base * temporal * environmental", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "渗透测试方法论", "code_template": "def calculate_cvss(base_score, temporal_factor, environmental_factor):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"9.0, 0.9, 1.0\", \"expected\": \"8.1\"}]", "solution": "def calculate_cvss(base_score, temporal_factor, environmental_factor):\n    return round(base_score * temporal_factor * environmental_factor, 1)", "hint": "三个因子相乘"},
        {"title": "实现安全配置检查器", "description": "编写函数check_security_config(config)，检查安全配置。\n\n检查: debug模式关闭、密码策略、会话超时\n返回配置问题列表", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "code_template": "def check_security_config(config):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"{debug:true,min_password_length:4}\", \"expected\": \"[debug_enabled, weak_password_policy]\"}]", "solution": "def check_security_config(config):\n    issues = []\n    if config.get('debug'): issues.append('debug_enabled')\n    if config.get('min_password_length', 0) < 8: issues.append('weak_password_policy')\n    if config.get('session_timeout', 0) > 3600: issues.append('session_timeout_too_long')\n    return issues", "hint": "逐项检查安全配置"},

        # ==================== 简答题 (25题) ====================
        {"title": "OWASP Top 10详解", "description": "列举并解释OWASP Top 10中的主要安全风险。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "OWASP Top 10", "solution": "主要风险: 1)注入(SQL/NoSQL/OS) 2)失效的认证 3)敏感数据泄露 4)XML外部实体(XXE) 5)失效的访问控制 6)安全配置错误 7)跨站脚本(XSS) 8)不安全的反序列化 9)使用含漏洞的组件 10)不足的日志和监控。每个风险都有特定的攻击方式和防护措施。"},
        {"title": "SQL注入防护方法", "description": "详细描述SQL注入的防护方法。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "SQL注入", "solution": "防护方法: 1)参数化查询/预编译语句(最有效) 2)使用ORM框架 3)输入验证(白名单) 4)最小权限原则(数据库用户权限) 5)存储过程 6)WAF(Web应用防火墙) 7)错误信息不暴露SQL细节 8)定期安全审计。核心原则: 永远不要拼接SQL语句。"},
        {"title": "XSS攻击与防护", "description": "详细描述XSS攻击的类型和防护方法。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "XSS", "solution": "类型: 反射型(URL参数注入)、存储型(数据库存储)、DOM型(前端JS处理)。防护: 1)输出编码(HTML/JS/URL编码) 2)Content-Security-Policy 3)HttpOnly Cookie 4)输入验证 5)使用安全框架(自动转义) 6)WAF。XSS防护的核心是对所有输出进行适当的编码。"},
        {"title": "CSRF攻击与防护", "description": "详细描述CSRF攻击的原理和防护方法。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "CSRF", "solution": "原理: 利用用户已认证的会话，诱使用户执行非预期操作。防护: 1)CSRF Token(每个请求唯一token) 2)SameSite Cookie属性 3)检查Referer/Origin头 4)双重Cookie验证 5)关键操作二次确认。CSRF防护的核心是确保请求来自合法来源。"},
        {"title": "渗透测试方法论", "description": "描述渗透测试的标准流程和方法论。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "渗透测试方法论", "solution": "流程: 1)信息收集(域名、IP、技术栈) 2)漏洞扫描(自动化工具) 3)漏洞验证(手动确认) 4)渗透利用(获取权限) 5)后渗透(横向移动) 6)报告编写。方法论: OWASP Testing Guide、PTES、OSSTMM。注意: 必须获得授权，遵守法律。"},
        {"title": "安全测试工具对比", "description": "对比常用安全测试工具的特点和适用场景。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全测试工具", "solution": "工具: Burp Suite(代理抓包、漏洞扫描)、OWASP ZAP(开源扫描器)、Nmap(端口扫描)、SQLMap(SQL注入)、Metasploit(渗透框架)。Burp Suite功能全面适合专业测试，ZAP免费适合入门，Nmap适合网络层扫描，SQLMap专注注入，Metasploit适合渗透。"},
        {"title": "安全编码规范", "description": "描述安全编码的主要规范和最佳实践。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全编码实践", "solution": "规范: 1)输入验证(白名单) 2)输出编码 3)参数化查询 4)最小权限原则 5)安全的密码存储(加盐哈希) 6)安全的会话管理 7)错误处理(不暴露细节) 8)日志审计 9)安全配置 10)依赖管理(及时更新)。核心原则: 永远不信任用户输入。"},
        {"title": "认证与授权安全", "description": "描述认证和授权的安全最佳实践。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "认证漏洞", "solution": "认证: 1)强密码策略 2)多因素认证 3)账户锁定机制 4)安全的密码重置 5)会话管理。授权: 1)最小权限原则 2)基于角色的访问控制 3)服务端验证(不依赖客户端) 4)防止越权(水平/垂直) 5)API权限检查。"},
        {"title": "敏感数据保护", "description": "描述敏感数据保护的方法和最佳实践。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "敏感信息泄露", "solution": "保护方法: 1)传输加密(HTTPS) 2)存储加密(密码加盐哈希) 3)数据脱敏(日志、测试环境) 4)最小化收集 5)访问控制 6)密钥管理 7)定期审计。注意: 密码不可逆加密、信用卡等PCI数据特殊处理、GDPR合规。"},
        {"title": "Web应用防火墙", "description": "描述WAF(Web应用防火墙)的作用和工作原理。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全测试工具", "solution": "WAF作用: 过滤恶意HTTP流量，防护SQL注入、XSS、CSRF等攻击。工作原理: 1)规则匹配(签名检测) 2)行为分析(异常检测) 3)机器学习(智能识别)。部署方式: 云WAF、硬件WAF、软件WAF。局限: 不能替代安全编码，可能误报。"},
        {"title": "安全测试与功能测试的区别", "description": "对比安全测试和功能测试的区别。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "渗透测试方法论", "solution": "区别: 功能测试验证系统是否按需求工作(正向)，安全测试验证系统是否能抵御攻击(逆向)。功能测试关注正确性，安全测试关注健壮性。功能测试用正常数据，安全测试用恶意数据。两者互补: 功能测试不能替代安全测试。"},
        {"title": "API安全测试", "description": "API接口安全测试应关注哪些方面？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "OWASP Top 10", "solution": "关注: 1)认证和授权(API Key/JWT/OAuth) 2)输入验证(参数类型、范围) 3)速率限制(防滥用) 4)数据加密(HTTPS) 5)错误处理(不暴露内部信息) 6)CORS配置 7)注入攻击 8)批量数据泄露 9)日志审计。工具: Postman、Burp Suite、OWASP ZAP。"},
        {"title": "移动端安全测试", "description": "移动端应用安全测试的特殊考虑。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "渗透测试方法论", "solution": "特殊考虑: 1)数据存储安全(本地存储加密) 2)通信安全(证书固定) 3)代码混淆(防逆向) 4)Root/越狱检测 5)组件安全(WebView) 6)权限管理 7)反编译保护 8)安全键盘。工具: Drozer(Android)、Objection(iOS)。"},
        {"title": "安全开发生命周期(SDL)", "description": "描述安全开发生命周期(SDL)的各阶段。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "渗透测试方法论", "solution": "SDL阶段: 1)需求: 安全需求分析 2)设计: 威胁建模 3)实现: 安全编码 4)验证: 安全测试 5)发布: 安全审查 6)响应: 安全事件响应。核心: 安全左移(越早发现越便宜)。Microsoft SDL是最知名的实践框架。"},
        {"title": "威胁建模", "description": "什么是威胁建模？如何进行？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "渗透测试方法论", "solution": "威胁建模是系统化识别安全威胁的方法。步骤: 1)绘制数据流图 2)识别威胁(STRIDE模型) 3)评估风险(DREAD评分) 4)制定防护措施 5)验证。STRIDE: Spoofing(欺骗)、Tampering(篡改)、Repudiation(抵赖)、Information Disclosure(信息泄露)、DoS(拒绝服务)、Elevation of Privilege(权限提升)。"},
        {"title": "安全测试自动化", "description": "如何实现安全测试自动化？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "安全测试", "knowledge_point": "安全测试工具", "solution": "自动化方式: 1)SAST(静态应用安全测试): 代码扫描 2)DAST(动态应用安全测试): 运行时扫描 3)IAST(交互式): 结合两者 4)SCA(软件成分分析): 依赖漏洞 5)CI/CD集成: 每次构建自动扫描 6)容器安全扫描。工具: SonarQube、Checkmarx、Snyk。"},
